Pfizer Signs Saudi Arabia Pharmaceutical Plant Deal, SPA Says

-- B y   G l e n   C a r e y
-- 
2011-10-04T11:59:31Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-04/pfizer-signs-saudi-arabia-pharmaceutical-plant-deal-spa-says.html
Pfizer Inc. (PFE)  signed an agreement to
open a pharmaceutical manufacturing plant in  Saudi Arabia , the
official  Saudi Press Agency  said.  The plant will begin production in 2015 and will employ 200
people in King Abdullah Economic City in Rabigh on the Red Sea
coast, the Riyadh-based  news service  reported, without saying
where it got the information. New York-based Pfizer signed the
agreement with the Saudi Arabian General Investment Authority,
the news service said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Glen Carey in Dubai at 
 gcarey8@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Andrew J. Barden at 
 barden@bloomberg.net  